  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7 and boil a kettle</p><p>Chop the <strong>sweet pointed pepper<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> in half lengthways, then deseed (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon)</p><p>Peel and chop <strong>half</strong> the<strong> red onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> </strong>into wedges then finely dice the <strong>remaining onion</strong></p><p>Drain the <strong>beetroot </strong>in a colander over the sink, then dice the <strong>drained beetroot</strong> very finely</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1684499246240-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1684499246240-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1684499246240-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1684499246240-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1684499246240-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped pepper</strong>, <strong>onion wedges</strong> and <strong>diced beetroot</strong> to a baking tray with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and a pinch of<strong> salt</strong></p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 15-20 min or until the veg is tender and slightly charred – this is your <strong>roasted veg</strong></p><p>Tip: Cooking for 4? Use 2 trays!</p><p>Combine the <strong>red wine vinegar</strong> and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong> in a large bowl with the <strong>diced onion </strong>– this is your <strong>quick-pickled onion</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1684499256599-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1684499256599-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1684499256599-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
