    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>bulgur wheat</strong> to a pot with plenty of <strong>boiled water</strong> (the same as you would for pasta)</p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 7-9 min or until tender with a slight bite</p><p>Once cooked, drain and rinse under a little <strong>cold running water </strong>to cool slightly, then return to the pot</p>",
