    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the roasted veg is ready, remove the tray<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> from the oven and set aside to cool slightly</p><p>Combine the <strong>courgette ribbons</strong> and the juice of 1/2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[1]</span> <strong>lemon </strong>in the reserved bowl with the <strong>roasted onion wedges</strong>, the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>ground</strong> <strong>sumac</strong>, a little <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>– this is your <strong>marinated courgette</strong></p>",
