      "instruction": "<p>Chop the <strong>toasted pittas</strong> into triangles</p><p>Serve the <strong>beetroot hummus</strong> topped with the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>roasted beetroot </strong>and crumble over the <strong>feta</strong></p><p>Serve the<strong> toasted pitta triangles</strong>, <strong>marinated courgette </strong>and <strong>tabbouleh</strong> to the side and top with the <strong>roasted pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
